summary: This is a single warpaint replacer for the 01 female head warpaint.  Its based on Keaira from Age of Conan
descriptionHtml:
======================================================================================
This is based on the character of Keaira from Age of Conan. I drew this up myself as I'm a big fan of that character. It will replace the 01 warpaint for females, so be aware that this is not a Stand Alone warpaint.

If someone would be kind enough to walk me through the best way to do a body paint, I'd be willing to complete the Keaira look with her arm and chest paint as well. But I haven't looked into Body Painting yet. Its possible now with Race Menu, is it not?

Anyway, if you're a fan of Keaira... I hope you enjoy this and if you hate it... well, I will be glad to throw this box of stray cats at you.
======================================================================================
